Chapter 1. Admin Guide

   Table of Contents

   1. Overview
   2. FIFO command syntax
   3. Dependencies

        3.1. Kamailio Modules
        3.2. External Libraries or Applications

   4. Parameters

        4.1. fifo_name (string)
        4.2. fifo_mode (integer)
        4.3. fifo_group (integer) fifo_group (string)
